<solution>
<p><ul><li>6.999861080229</li></ul></p><p><m>\displaystyle{P}{\left({t}\right)}={750}{e}^{{{0.18}{t}}}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle{2644}={750}{e}^{{{0.18}{t}}}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle\frac{{2644}}{{750}}={e}^{{{0.18}{t}}}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle{\ln{{\left(\frac{{2644}}{{750}}\right)}}}={0.18}{t}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle\frac{{\ln{{\left(\frac{{2644}}{{750}}\right)}}}}{{0.18}}={t}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle{t}={6.999861080229}</m></p>
</solution>
